Monday January 30 Mxolisi decides to come clean. Mastermind and Ayanda hear from Smangele. Sibahle hopes for a reunion. Ayanda tells Mastermind that Smangele is missing. Mondli confirms that the bones belong to Nkosinathi. Thobile, Fikile and GC feel for Manzuza. Tuesday January 31 Mondli, Jabulile and Mxolisi are all after the same thing, which they want to use for different reasons. Ayanda has a surprise waiting for him, news that he can t wait to share with everyone. MaNgcobo tells Mxolisi not to be stupid when he wants to confess to MaNzuza. Ayanda and Mastermind arrive and see that Sma has given birth.